sub_title: HelloFresh Benelux Growth Marketing Intern      International Business Undergraduate
summary:
üìå Dedicated young professional with clear values and strong work ethics.¬†Every day, I strive to be a part of the change. My undergraduate studies have provided me with solid knowledge related to 4 major business fields. In addition to that, I have gained valuable experience while working on a variety of projects for companies. Trade marketing, sales, negotiation, procurement and Incoterms are some of fields that I am interested in. 

üó∫ Besides my studies, I am part of a student association in the events management department. Organising, planning and creating have always been a huge passion of mine. Additionally, I take part in European student projects related to current topics in the social and academic aspects, some of which were recently held in Lisbon and Istanbul. The international setting has highly benefited me in terms of networking, critical thinking, sharpening my communication and presenting skills. Because of that, I‚Äôm a very open-minded and multipotentialite person.

üèÜ It is important to keep the balance and my way of doing it is while spending time in nature, hiking or exploring new places. Huge passion of mine are functional sports, mindfulness and health lifestyle.

üåç I love meeting new people, exchanging experiences and learning new things, so feel free to say hello and share a story with me. And remember, your mind is the key to success!
